  "texts": [
    "Human annotators followed annotation guidelines foot_1 to assign none, one, or multiple annotations to each sample.",
    "These annotations consisted of cue words that invoke speech events and roles (Addr, Evidence, Medium, Message, Source, Topic, PTC) associated with that event.",
    "While the cue is mandatory for each annotation, roles are context-dependent and may be absent.",
    "Figure 1 shows example annotations.",
    "The Shared Task consisted of two subtasks: Full Annotation (Subtask 1) and Role Detection (Subtask 2) (Rehbein et al., 2023) Table 2: Number of speeches, samples (units of analysis), and annotations for each dataset."
